&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://gitee.com/rogeeerluo/PicGoPics/raw/master/image-20210825172658541.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20210825172658541&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
$$
\dot A_{vH}= \frac{1}{1+j\omega R_2C_2}=\frac{1}{1+j(f/f_H)}
\space  when \space f_H=\frac{1}{2\pi R_2C_2}
\\ |\dot A _{vM}|=\frac {1}{\sqrt{1+(f/f_H)^2}},\space \varphi =-arctan(f/f_H)
$$


&lt;/p&gt;
