C_{M1}=(1+g_mR_L&amp;#x27;)C_{gd},\ C_{M2}可忽略 
\newline R_{si}&amp;#x27;=R_{Si}//R_g
\newline R_L&amp;#x27;=R_d//R_L
\newline |A_{vsM} ·f_H| \approx \frac{1}{2\pi R_{si}C_{gd}}
